{"name":"Turn Undead (inacabado)","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"classfeatures.html","source":"PHB","hash":"turn%20undead_cleric_phb_2_phb"},"favtab":{"isFavorite":false},"siftoolkit":{"SIFData":{"ignoreDuration":false,"texture":"","useTexture":false,"alpha":50,"coneOrigin":1,"loopAnimations":true,"playTemplateAudio":false,"playDamageAudio":false,"clip":"","volume":100}},"midi-qol":{"onUseMacroName":"[postActiveEffects]ItemMacro","effectActivation":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"reaches 0 charges: it crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jKKYsvzCW3OsUvIv"},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false,"ignoreTotalCover":false},"scene-packer":{"hash":"370b86081c4296b5c0f9db989f6042fbf875e506","sourceId":"Item.BNe77rQ4Xz6mqVq0"},"itemacro":{"macro":{"data":{"_id":null,"name":"Turn Undead (inacabado)","type":"script","author":"QwT9izJ4aW8QVTjo","img":"icons/svg/dice-target.svg","scope":"global","command":"// falta testar o CR pra matar\n// se o primeiro do canvas passar, nenhum outro faz o teste.\nlet targetList = args[0].targets;\nif(targetList.length === 0) return {};\nlet saveType = \"wis\";\nlet saved = [];\nlet failed = [].actor;\nconst actorD = (await fromUuid(args[0].tokenUuid)).actor || args[0].actor;\nconst DC = actorD.data.data.abilities.wis.dc;\nlet effectData = {\n        label : \"Channel Divinity: Turn Undead\",\n        icon : \"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/yellow_19.jpg\",\n        duration: {rounds: 10}\n          }\n\nfor(let target of targetList) {\n        if (target.actor.data.data.details.type?.value.toLowerCase().includes(\"undead\") || target.actor.data.data.details.race?.toLowerCase().includes(\"undead\")) {\n\t\tlet save = await MidiQOL.socket().executeAsGM(\"rollAbility\", { request: \"save\", targetUuid: target.actor.uuid, ability: saveType});\n    \t\tif(save.total < DC) {\n       \t\t\tawait MidiQOL.socket().executeAsGM(\"createEffects\", {actorUuid: target.uuid, effects: [effectData]});\n\t\tawait target.update({\"data.attributes.hp.value\": 0})       \n\t\t} else {return{}}\n} }","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}}},"rest-recovery":{"data":{"recovery":{"enabled":false}}}},"_id":"Ca9Rbl4HNnjCMJ2F","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As an action, you present your holy symbol and speak a prayer censuring the undead. Each undead that can see or hear you within 30 feet of you must make a Wisdom saving throw. If the creature fails its saving throw, it is turned for 1 minute or until it takes any damage.</p><p>A turned creature must spend its turns trying to move as far away from you as it can, and it can't willingly move to a space within 30 feet of you. It also can't take reactions. For its action, it can use only the @action[Dash] action or try to escape from an effect that prevents it from moving. If there's nowhere to move, the creature can use the @action[Dodge] action.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"\"@raceOrType\".includes(\"undead\")"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cylinder"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"charges","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"C